COCA-COLA Co. (Atlanta) -- Anton Amon and George Gourlay were elected vice presidents of this soft-drink company.
Mr. Amon, 46 years old, is the company's director of quality assurance; most recently, he served as vice president, operations, for Coca-Cola Enterprises.
Mr. Gourlay, 48, is manager for corporate manufacturing operations; he was assistant vice president at the company. 

